        "TileImage": "$($repository 0c804787-93f3-49e4-8f11-f445f5b35737).Image",
        "Description": "Squidward stood where PatrikkiBobi had been, the ocean feeling emptier than before. The silence lingered, heavy and unfamiliar. He missed the laughter and the strange, lively presence that once filled the reef.\r\rDays passed, and Squidward returned to his routine—playing his clarinet and watching the tides. It wasn’t the same, but life moved on.\r\rIn quiet moments, he still paused to remember, carrying the sadness and the memories together.",
